verbose_text: Additionally to the induction of the FIH / RIPK4 complex, we noticed that chaperones such as HSP90 and members of the T-complex protein complex decreased their association with RIPK4 upon FIH overexpression (XREF_FIG C and XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY A), as did three members of the SCF complex, BTRC, FBXW11, and SKP1 (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY B).
